  <Summary>Conan and his raiders attack a caravan but find only a girl and a sabre-tooth cat for loot.

Conan travels to the city of Akbitana to discover the secret of the mysterious Citadel that has appeared there.

Conan awakens inside the Citadel, captive of Shamash-Shum-Ukin who plans to use him as a sacrifice to the Well of Time.

Conan and Alhambra escape from the Well of Time and from the Citadel as it comes tumbling down.</Summary>
